{"tid":1096619,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【清明父子照】藝術家挖先父骸骨拍片影相 網民：炒作無底線！","createTime":"2019-04-07T23:34:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-08T08:41:43.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"18cd33cb6c5fe39fc87f15bfdeffe1607c868dea","tid":1096619,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T23:34:57.000Z","msg":"清明節掃墓，用意是不忘先人，但內地一名新進的行為藝術家，於清明節這天把父親的屍骨挖出，和骸骨拍攝一系列「父子照」，並上載到微博。不過，這輯照片和影片已全被刪除。<br />\n行為藝術家司原逐冀今日在微博上傳一段影片，紀錄家人為父親遷墳的過程。司原逐冀表示，父親因病去世時才28歲，當時他還年幼。在撿骨這一天，他擔心家人無法接受他想裸身和父親合照的想法，決定直接和撿骨師溝通，並由他的妻子擔任攝影師，拍攝這系列照片。<br />\n畫面上傳網絡後，有網民表示理解，還有人覺得看完影片後有點心酸。不過也有人覺得難以理解，甚至批評這名行為藝術家純粹是為了炒作。<br />\n網民講乜：<br />\nLimoncello：很勇敢，有些心酸孤獨。<br />\n種棵樹猴面包樹：印尼人的風俗每年都會把去世的親人挖出來合影。<br />\npinpinil：沒必要！<br />\n幸運丿四葉草：行為對錯暫且不說，光發出來在公眾視野就真的變態！！<br />\n劉米拉-milla：為了炒作已經沒有底線了。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190407/large/1554621494_c878.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190407%2Flarge%2F1554621494_c878.jpg&h=934e3ab7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190407/large/1554621496_b2c6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190407%2Flarge%2F1554621496_b2c6.jpg&h=1f8ac2bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190407/59459629\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190407%2F59459629&d=Qy2hiQzhAVWh7XuXj3aMUQvpIPIfgcH1aomtamkqoQA%3D&h=4c1f9de5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190407%2F59459629&h=876f78a2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190407/59459629</a>"},{"pid":"c65e7cae7edda9b372807790d4fd129f5d4ae18b","tid":1096619,"uid":167032,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":